Grok Resume skill extraction

This package contains source artifacts extracted from the locally installed
Grok Build 0.2.106 distribution, build bde89716f679, on 2026-07-22.

The byte-identical source snapshot is stored under:

  raw/grok-0.2.106-bde89716/

The active shared copies under shared/resume-session/ preserve CORE.md and
session_reader.py byte-for-byte. The two installable wrapper SKILL.md files
under skills/ remove Grok's unsupported `argument-hint` frontmatter key and
express argument handling in cross-platform wording; their behavior and
shared-reader contract are otherwise unchanged.

The open-source Grok Build repository does not contain these bundled skill
bodies. Runtime integration evidence is pinned to xai-org/grok-build commit
3af4d5d39897855bdcc74f23e690024a5dc05573, while the extracted bodies are
pinned independently by the installed build identifier and MANIFEST.sha256.

